
@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>403 - Erişim Engellendi</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #282828;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #e94560;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #00f5d4;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        a {
            color: #00f5d4;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

            a:hover {
                color:white;
            }

        .btn-back {
            background-color: #00f5d4;
            color: #121212;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .btn-back:hover {
                background-color: #e94560;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>403</h1>
        <h2>Erişim Engellendi</h2>
        <p>Bu sayfaya erişim izniniz bulunmamaktadır. Lütfen geri dönün veya yetkili kişilere başvurun.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-back">Anasayfaya Dön</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
